<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>

        <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
        <section class="bm-hero">
            <div class="bm-hero-inner">
                <h1 class="bm-hero-title">Simple, Transparent Pricing —<br>For Every Restaurant</h1>
                <p class="bm-hero-subtitle">We designed Bhojan Mitra pricing to be clear, fair, and tied to real value — so you only pay for what grows your business.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
        <section class="bm-features" id="features">
            <div class="bm-features-inner">

                <div class="bm-badge">POS machine</div>

                <!-- Feature 1 -->
                <div class="bm-feature-row">
                    <div class="bm-feature-text">
                        <h3 class="bm-feature-title">Natural Language Understanding</h3>
                        <p class="bm-feature-desc">Our point-of-sale system offers natural language ordering with multilingual support, making it easy for your staff to communicate with customers from all backgrounds. It also provides smart upsells, suggesting additional items based on the customer's order. This helps to increase revenue and improve the customer experience.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bm-feature-img">
                        <img src="/images/illus-voice.png" alt="Natural Language Understanding" width="220" height="220">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 2 -->
                <div class="bm-feature-row bm-feature-row--reverse">
                    <div class="bm-feature-img">
                        <img src="/images/illus-ai.png" alt="IoT Integrations" width="220" height="220">
                    </div>
                    <div class="bm-feature-text">
                        <h3 class="bm-feature-title">IoT Integrations</h3>
                        <p class="bm-feature-desc">Connect printers, displays, and kitchen devices for seamless routing and streamlined operations. Our system ensures efficient communication between all your hardware. Experience fewer errors and faster service with integrated device management.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 3 -->
                <div class="bm-feature-row">
                    <div class="bm-feature-text">
                        <h3 class="bm-feature-title">Inventory Management</h3>
                        <p class="bm-feature-desc">Optimize your inventory with real-time stock tracking. Configure low-stock alerts to minimize waste and prevent shortages. Our system helps you maintain optimal levels automatically.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bm-feature-img">
                        <img src="/images/illus-analytics.png" alt="Inventory Management" width="220" height="220">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 4 -->
                <div class="bm-feature-row bm-feature-row--reverse">
                    <div class="bm-feature-img">
                        <img src="/images/illus-dashboard.png" alt="Secure Cloud Sync" width="220" height="220">
                    </div>
                    <div class="bm-feature-text">
                        <h3 class="bm-feature-title">Secure Cloud Sync</h3>
                        <p class="bm-feature-desc">Our point-of-sale system provides cloud backups, real-time sync across terminals, and secure data storage. You can rest assured that your data is safe and accessible. Focus on your customers, and let us handle the technology.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
        <section class="bm-faq">
            <div class="bm-faq-inner">
                <span class="bm-faq-eyebrow">FAQ</span>
                <h2 class="bm-faq-title"><span class="bm-faq-muted">Questions</span> Operators Ask Most</h2>

                <div class="bm-faq-list">

                    <details class="bm-faq-item bm-faq-item--open" open>
                        <summary class="bm-faq-question">
                            What makes Bhojan Mitra different from other POS systems?
                            <span class="bm-faq-icon"></span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="bm-faq-answer">Bhojan Mitra is voice-first. Orders can be spoken in multiple Indian languages, modifiers are captured automatically, and IoT routing sends tickets to the right kitchen station without manual steps.</p>
                    </details>

                    <details class="bm-faq-item">
                        <summary class="bm-faq-question">
                            Can Bhojan Mitra replace my existing POS machine?
                            <span class="bm-faq-icon"></span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="bm-faq-answer">Yes. Bhojan Mitra runs on browsers, tablets, and our dedicated POS machine. We map printers and kitchen displays so you can migrate without downtime.</p>
                    </details>

                    <details class="bm-faq-item">
                        <summary class="bm-faq-question">
                            How long does pilot onboarding take?
                            <span class="bm-faq-icon"></span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="bm-faq-answer">Most pilot restaurants are up and running within 2–3 days. We handle setup, menu import, and staff training as part of the onboarding package.</p>
                    </details>

                    <details class="bm-faq-item">
                        <summary class="bm-faq-question">
                            Does the POS work if the internet drops?
                            <span class="bm-faq-icon"></span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="bm-faq-answer">Offline fallback mode keeps billing and order capture running locally. Orders sync automatically when connectivity is restored.</p>
                    </details>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
        <section class="bm-cta">
            <div class="bm-cta-inner">
                <h2 class="bm-cta-title">See <span class="bm-cta-highlight">Bhojan Mitra</span> in Action</h2>
                <p class="bm-cta-sub">Join the pilot to experience voice ordering, IoT routing, and analytics tailored to your restaurant before our public launch.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js?v=<%= locals.assetVersion %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
